She will not back down from an argument. 
In this video, she tried to convince her dad that the proper way to count to five is one, two, three, five. She keeps skipping four!! You can listen to Johnjay and Rich every weekday morning! Get your #LoveUp shirt NOW! www.loveupshirt.com Contact
